AI SDK › Prompts › Message Prompts › Assistant Messages › Example: Assistant message with tool call content

```ts highlight="7-14"
const result = await generateText({
  model: __MODEL__,
  messages: [
    { role: 'user', content: 'How many calories are in this block of cheese?' },
    {
      role: 'assistant',
